          "LessonTitle": "Lesson 1: Introduction to Neural Networks",
          "Content": "In this lesson, we will introduce the concept of neural networks and their applications. We will discuss the basic structure of a neural network, including input, hidden, and output layers. Additionally, we will explore the different types of neural networks, such as feedforward and recurrent networks."
        },
